a.n: Mr Bean: The Animated Series - Elements I (222)

p.k: Keyboard Capers Determined to play the piano, Mr Bean finds a tune in his heart and sausages for fingers.
p.d: Mr. Bean is joined by his trusty sidekick Teddy his reliable MINI and his grumpy landlady Mrs Wicket not forgetting her evil one-eyed cat Scrapper.
